ttp_template:
<group name="critical_major_minor_warning">
Critical  : {{CRITICAL | ORPHRASE}}
Major  : {{MAJOR | ORPHRASE}}
Minor  : {{MINOR | ORPHRASE}}
Warning  : {{WARNING | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
textfsm_template:
Value CRITICAL (\d+)
Value MAJOR (\d+)
Value MINOR (\d+)
Value WARNING (\d+)

Start
  ^Critical\s*:\s*${CRITICAL}\s*$$
  ^Major\s*:\s*${MAJOR}\s*$$
  ^Minor\s*:\s*${MINOR}\s*$$
  ^Warning\s*:\s*${WARNING}\s*$$ -> Record
